in those days for them also. She was a very close friend of my first wife and her mother was a "Young" a distant relative of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9769733\charrsid4850714 Young\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid411975\charrsid4850714  mentioned all of whom were connected with the Steel and Iron Trades in Co. Durham.
